from PyPDF2 import PdfReader

pdf_path = '/workspace/benchmark/datasets/19-Native-Sparse-Attention/NSA/paper.pdf'
reader = PdfReader(pdf_path)

# Extract the first 5 pages for inspection
paper_text = ''
for i, page in enumerate(reader.pages[:5]):
    paper_text += page.extract_text() + '\n---PAGE BREAK---\n'

print(paper_text[:3000])
